Individual




L. Heath Sampson



Mr. L. H. Sampson is on the Board of Directors at Advanced Emissions Solutions, Inc., ADA-ES, Inc. and Clean Coal Solutions LLC. Mr. Sampson was previously employed as Chief Financial Officer by First Data Corp. and Chief Financial Officer & Senior Vice President by SquareTwo Financial Corp. He received his undergraduate degree from the University of Denver and a graduate degree from the University of Denver.



