L. Heath Sampson: Executive Profile & Biography - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 28, 2017 1:45 PM ET
Chemicals

Company Overview of Advanced Emissions Solutions, Inc.



SnapshotPeople 




OverviewBoard MembersCommittees



Executive Profile
L. Heath Sampson  Chief Executive Officer, President, Principal Financial Officer, Treasurer and Director , Advanced Emissions Solutions, Inc.AgeTotal Calculated CompensationThis person is connected to 2 Board Members in 2 different organizations across 2 different industries.See Board Relationships46$4,106,941As of Fiscal Year 2016
Background

		Mr. L. Heath Sampson has been the Chief Executive Officer and President of Advanced Emissions Solutions, Inc. since April 1, 2015 and serves as its Treasurer since August 27, 2014. Mr. Sampson has been Principal Financial Officer of Advanced Emissions Solutions, Inc. since August 1, 2016. He served as the Chief Financial Officer at Advanced Emissions Solutions, Inc. from August 27, 2014 to April 1, 2015. He served as Chief Financial Officer of First Data Financial Services. ... Mr. Sampson served as the Chief Financial Officer and Senior Vice President of SquareTwo Financial Corporation from September 1, 2009 to August 1, 2014 and from September 2009 to August 1, 2014 respectively and served as its and Principal Accounting Officer until August 1, 2014. Mr. Sampson joined SquareTwo Financial from First Data Corp., where he served as Chief Financial Officer of the $2.5 billion Financial Services subsidiary since 2008. He joined First Data in 2002 and served as Vice President of risk, control and audit from 2002 to 2006. He served as Chief Financial Officer of First Data's Integrated Payment Systems division since 2006 and its Chief Financial Officer of its Innovative Payments Group since 2007. He served as a Senior Manager in financial audit, business consulting and risk consulting at Arthur Andersen LLP, which he joined in 1994. He has been a Director of Advanced Emissions Solutions, Inc. since 2015. He serves as Director of Clean Coal Solutions, LLC and oversees all financial and certain operational matters, including financial planning and analysis, tax, treasury, accounting, internal audit and information technology. He is a Member of the Colorado AICPA and is Six Sigma Greenbelt-Black Belt Trained. He is a Certified Public Accountant He received his Bachelors of Business Administration in Accounting and a Masters of Accountancy from the University of Denver.Read Full Background




